@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title HPA Configurable Tolerance (K8s 1.34 Beta)

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<scale>> #90EE90
  BackgroundColor<<noscale>> #FFB6C1
  BackgroundColor<<zone>> #FFEFD5
}

rectangle "Comportement par defaut (10%)" as default {
  rectangle "Target: 50% CPU" as target1
  rectangle "Zone morte\n45% - 55%" as zone1 <<zone>>
  rectangle "Current: 52%" as current1

  target1 -down-> zone1
  current1 -down-> zone1 : Pas de scaling

  note right of zone1
    **Probleme grands deployments:**
    10% de 1000 pods = 100 pods
    Oscillations importantes
  end note
}

rectangle "Tolerance configurable" as custom {
  rectangle "Scale Up: tolerance 5%" as up <<scale>> {
    note as upnote
      behavior:
        scaleUp:
          tolerance: 5%

      Scale si > 52.5%
    end note
  }

  rectangle "Scale Down: tolerance 15%" as down <<noscale>> {
    note as downnote
      behavior:
        scaleDown:
          tolerance: 15%

      Scale si < 42.5%
    end note
  }
}

note bottom of custom
  **Configuration complete:**
  ```yaml
  apiVersion: autoscaling/v2
  kind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler
  spec:
    behavior:
      scaleUp:
        tolerance: 5%
      scaleDown:
        tolerance: 15%
  ```

  **Resultat:**
  - Scale up reactif (5%)
  - Scale down conservateur (15%)
  - Evite oscillations
end note

legend right
  |= Scenario |= Scale Up |= Scale Down |
  | Defaut | 10% | 10% |
  | Reactif | 5% | 15% |
  | Conservateur | 15% | 20% |
endlegend

footer **KEP-4951:** Tolerance HPA par instance, asymetrique up/down
@enduml
